{
  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_0' aria-label=\" Mohit Kumar versus State of Uttar Pradesh and Ors. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('0','2025','2025_6_499_512','2025INSC704'); ><font size='4'> <strong>MOHIT KUMAR<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>STATE OF UTTAR PRADESH AND ORS. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 6 S.C.R. 499</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 704</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010002082025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : DIPANKAR DATTA, MANMOHAN</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Issue arose whether Uttar Pradesh Police Recruitment and Promotion Board was bound to accept the OBC certificates submitted by aspirants which, admittedly, were not in the format prescribed in the recruitment notification. Headnotes&dagger; Service law &ndash; Recruitment in the format prescribed &ndash; Requirement, if mandatory &ndash; Appellant-candidate applied for the post of sub-inspector and was called for examination &ndash; However, his representation rejected on the ground that he did not submit OBC certificate in the prescribed format and thus,<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 14-05-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 5233/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Disposed off</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('0','2025','2025_6_499_512','2025INSC704','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('0','2025','2025_6_499_512','2025INSC704','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('0','2025','2025_6_499_512','2025INSC704');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('0','2025','2025_6_499_512','2025INSC704','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
